('Sonic Forces', 'playstation 4', ' Platform game, Action-adventure game', 'single player','E 10+', 'Sega', 'Hardlight', 2017-11-07, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://image.api.playstation.com/cdn/UP0177/CUSA05637_00/vfs1Nf9GvyNIGBRqXMB9MGr3WMMmXVkJ.png?w=1024&thumb=false', 'In SONIC FORCES, the evil Dr. Eggman has conquered much of the world with help from a powerful and mysterious new villain named Infinite. Now, you must assist Sonic and build an army to reclaim the world as they fight against chaos and destruction.'),
('Jump Force', 'playstation 4', 'Fighting game, Adventure game', 'Multiplayer and single-player', 'teen adolescents', ' Namco Bandai Games America Inc.', 'Spike Chunsoft', 2019-02-15, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/0c/Jumpforcegame.jpg', 'When the real world collides with many of the Shōnen Jump universes, humanity is invaded by the "Venoms", an army of mind-controlled villains led by Kane and Galena. In order to fight back, many heroes are recruited to join the "Jump Force" under the leadership of Director Glover and his A.I. partner Navigator. But a suspicious figure is using both the Jump Force and the Venoms as an attempt to gain a mysterious artifact and merge all worlds into one.'),
('Little Nightmares Complete Edition', 'PlayStation 4', 'Puzzle, Adventure game, Platform game, Survival horror, adventure', 'single-player', 'teen adolescents', ' Bandai Namco Entertainment ', 'Tarsier Studios', 2017-10-26, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://image.api.playstation.com/vulcan/ap/rnd/202204/1908/pam5dUS6w13ovToXCy8mcRZ6.png', 'Little Nightmares Complete Edition is a 2017 puzzle-platformer game developed by Tarsier Studios and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment. The game follows Six, a young girl who is trapped in the Maw, a dark and twisted world inhabited by monstrous creatures. Players must guide Six through the Maw, solving puzzles and avoiding the creatures in order to escape.'),
('Naruto Shippuden: Ultimate Ninja Storm 4', 'playstation 4', 'Fighting game, Action-adventure game', 'Single-player and multiplayer', 'teen adolescents', 'Bandai Namco Entertainment', 'CyberConnect2', 2016-02-04, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://cdn.dlcompare.com/game_tetiere/upload/gameimage/file/7442.jpeg', ' NARUTO SHIPPUDEN™: Ultimate Ninja® STORM 4, a broad set of Ninja Skills will be yours to use against the fiercest foes you`ll ever encounter. Massive attacks in the form of secret techniques, energetic evolutions with the “Awakening”, the inimitable shurikens & kunais and a unique playstyle for each ninja!'),
('Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Hinokami Chronicles', 'PlayStation 4', ' Fighting, action', ' Single-player and multiplayer', 'teen adolescents', 'Sega, Aniplex', ' CyberConnect2', 2021-10-14, TRUE, FALSE , 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/40/Demon_Slayer_Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_%E2%80%93_The_Hinokami_Chronicles_box_art.jpg', 'Follow the story from Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Tanjiro Kamado, Unwavering Resolve Arc—where Tanjiro joins the Demon Slayer Corps— to Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba- The Movie: Mugen Train featuring the Flame Hashira, Kyojuro Rengoku!Players can choose from a roster of over 20 characters to battle in 3D arenas. The game also features a story mode that follows the events of the anime series.'),
('God of War', 'PlayStation 4', 'Action-Adventure', 'single-player', 'Mature', 'Santa Monica Studio', 'Sony Interactive Entertainment', 2018-04-20, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/a7/God_of_War_4_cover.jpg', 'God of War is a 2018 action-adventure game developed by Santa Monica Studio and published by Sony Interactive Entertainment. The game is the eighth installment in the God of War series, and the sequel to 2010''s God of War III. The game follows Kratos, the former Greek god of war, as he sets out on a journey to the Norse realm of Midgard with his son Atreus.'),
('Super Smash Bros Ultimate', 'Nintendo Switch', 'Fighting', '8', 'Everyone 10+', 'Nintendo', 'Nintendo', 2018-12-07, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/c_fill,w_1200/q_auto:best/f_auto/dpr_2.0/ncom/en_US/games/switch/s/super-smash-bros-ultimate-switch/hero','Super Smash Bros. Ultimate is a 2018 crossover fighting game developed by Sora Ltd. and published by Nintendo. The game is the fifth installment in the Super Smash Bros. series, and features characters from various Nintendo, third-party, and indie franchises. Players can battle each other in 2D arenas, and can also team up in 2v2 matches. A powerful & unknown enemy has attacked - and won. Hundreds of video game characters from past Nintendo games have been turned to spirits by Galeem and his army of Master Hands. Only Kirby has escaped the initial attack, riding a star. Now Kirby must venture by himself and discover the nature of the World of Light, as he attempts to free the other fighters, which have been turned into mindless puppets by Galeem.'),
('The Last of Us Part 1', 'PlayStation 4', 'Action-Adventure', 'single-player', 'Mature', 'Naughty Dog', 'Sony Interactive Entertainment', 2013-06-14, TRUE, FALSE,'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d5/The_Last_of_Us_Cover_Art.png','The Last of Us is an action-adventure survival horror video game developed by Naughty Dog and published by Sony Computer Entertainment. It was released for the PlayStation 3 worldwide on June 14, 2013. Players control Joel, a smuggler tasked with escorting a teenage girl, Ellie, across a post-apocalyptic United States.'),
('The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild', 'Nintendo Switch', 'Action-Adventure', '1', 'Everyone 10+', 'Nintendo', 'Nintendo', 2017-03-03, TRUE, FALSE,'https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/ar_16:9,b_auto:border,c_lpad/b_white/f_auto/q_auto/dpr_2.0/c_scale,w_900/ncom/en_US/games/switch/t/the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-switch/hero','The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild is a 2017 action-adventure game developed and published by Nintendo. The game is the sequel to 2011''s The Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword. The game follows Link, a Hylian knight, as he sets out to save Princess Zelda and Hyrule from the evil Calamity Ganon. Forget everything you know about The Legend of Zelda games. Step into a world of discovery, exploration, and adventure in The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, a boundary-breaking new game in the acclaimed series. Travel across vast fields, through forests, and to mountain peaks as you discover what has become of the kingdom of Hyrule in this stunning Open-Air Adventure. Now on Nintendo Switch, your journey is freer and more open than ever. Take your system anywhere, and adventure as Link any way you like.'),
('DragonBall 2 XENOVERSE', 'playstation 4', 'Fighting game', '2-4', 'teen adolescents', 'Bandai Namco Entertainment', 'Dimps', 2015-02-24, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e8/Dragon_Ball_Xenoverse_2_cover.jpg/220px-Dragon_Ball_Xenoverse_2_cover.jpg', 'DragonBall 2 XENOVERSE is an action RPG set in the DragonBall universe. Players create their own custom character and travel through time to fight against various enemies, including Frieza, Cell, and Majin Buu. The game features a variety of fighting styles, as well as a robust character customization system'),
('Call of DUTY Ghosts', 'playstation 4', 'First-person shooter', '1-12', 'Mature', 'Activision', 'Infinity Ward', 2013-11-05, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/8a/Call_of_Duty_Ghosts_cover.jpg/220px-Call_of_Duty_Ghosts_cover.jpg', 'Call of Duty Ghosts is a first-person shooter set in the near future. Players take on the role of members of the Ghosts, a special forces team that is tasked with fighting against a terrorist organization. The game features a variety of new gameplay mechanics, including a dynamic weather system and a dog companion that can be used to attack enemies.'),
('UNCHARTED a thief''s END 4', 'playstation 4', 'Action-Adventure', '1-3', 'Mature', 'Sony Computer Entertainment', 'Naughty Dog', 2016-05-10, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c5/Uncharted_4_A_Thief_s_End_cover.jpg/220px-Uncharted_4_A_Thief_s_End_cover.jpg', 'UNCHARTED a thief''s END 4 is an action-adventure game that serves as the conclusion to the Uncharted series. Players take on the role of Nathan Drake, a treasure hunter who is searching for the lost city of Shambhala. The game features a variety of new gameplay mechanics, including a grappling hook and a rope swing.'),
('DESTINY the taken king', 'playstation 4', 'First-person shooter', '1-12', 'Teen', 'Activision', 'Bungie', 2015-09-15, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c9/Destiny_The_Taken_King_cover.jpg/220px-Destiny_The_Taken_King_cover.jpg', 'Destiny the taken king is an expansion pack for the video game Destiny. The expansion pack introduces a new story campaign, new enemies, and new weapons and armor. The game also introduces a new raid, which is a challenging cooperative activity that can be played with up to six players.'),
