('Call of Duty Black OPS 3','playstation 4','First-person shooter','1-4','M','Activision','Treyarch',2015-11-06, TRUE, FALSE,'https://dummyimage.com/400x400/6e6c6e/e9e9f5.png&text=No+Image','Call of Duty Black OPS 3 is a first-person shooter video game developed by Treyarch and published by Activision. It is the eleventh installment in the Call of Duty series and the sequel to Call of Duty: Black Ops II. The game was released worldwide on November 6, 2015, for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One. In Call of Duty Black OPS 3, players take control of a customizable character who is part of a black ops unit. The game features a single-player campaign, a multiplayer mode, and a cooperative mode called Zombies. The single-player campaign takes place in the year 2065 and follows a group of black ops soldiers who are tasked with stopping a global terrorist threat. The multiplayer mode features traditional deathmatch and objective-based game modes, as well as a new mode called "Black Ops Ops". The cooperative mode, Zombies, is a survival mode where players must work together to defeat waves of zombies.The game''s multiplayer mode features a new system called "Specialists", which allows players to choose from a variety of characters with unique abilities.'),
('Madden 22','playstation 5','Sports','1-2','E','Electronic Arts','EA Tiburon', 2021-08-20, TRUE, FALSE, 'https://dummyimage.com/400x400/6e6c6e/e9e9f5.png&text=No+Image','Madden 22 is a sports video game developed by EA Tiburon and published by Electronic Arts. It is the 34th installment in the Madden NFL series and the successor to Madden NFL 21. The game was released worldwide on August 20, 2021, for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S. In Madden 22, players take control of a NFL team and compete against other teams in a variety of game modes, including exhibition games, regular season games, and the playoffs. The game also features a new mode called "Face of the Franchise" where players can create their own player and rise through the ranks of the NFL.Madden 22 features a new physics engine that allows for more realistic gameplay. The game also introduces a new mode called "The Yard", which is a 3v3 street football mode.'),
